-- Weidmann Warns Draghi of Euro-System Risks in Letter, FAZ Says
-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 2012-02-29T20:46:06Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-29/weidmann-warns-draghi-of-euro-system-risks-in-letter-faz-says.html
Bundesbank President Jens Weidmann
has warned European Central Bank President  Mario Draghi  about
growing euro-system risks and called for a return to the safety
rules that applied before the financial crisis,  Frankfurter
Allgemeine Zeitung  said in a preview of a story that will run
tomorrow, citing a letter from Weidmann to Draghi.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Niklas Magnusson in Hamburg at 
 nmagnusson1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Angela Cullen at 
 acullen8@bloomberg.net  